snippet.title: Megaman Zero Online 0.1.6 teaser
snippet.description:
Download: https://warrior555mainsganon.github.io/MMZOnline/
After 10 major updates, Dataroom's reign has come to an end. A new map shall come forth, a vestige of an once bustling civilization. Coming soon... In MEGAMAN ZERO ONLINE: UPDATE 0.1.6.
Discord: https://discord.gg/X2ctJHypam
Features implemented so far for 0.1.6:
-New map
-Rising slash
-Hit particle effects
-Emotes
-And more...
